Name: pyavalanche
Version: 0.6.0
Summary: Python OO API package to automate Spirent Avalanche traffic generator
Home-page: https://github.com/shmir/PyAvalanche/
Author: Yoram Shamir
Author-email: yoram@ignissoft.com
